OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,FIsraeli strikes have killed at least
OL,7,F14 people in southern Lebanon as
OL,8,FIsrael steps up its military campaign
OL,9,Fagainst Hezbollah ahead of key talks
OL,10,Fin Washington.
OL,12,FSeveral others were injured in the
OL,13,Fstrikes on Sidon on Thursday,
OL,14,Faccording to Lebanon's state-run
OL,15,FNational News Agency.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, the Israeli military said
OL,18,Fone soldier was killed in a drone
OL,19,Fattack by Hezbollah in northern Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
