OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780002672
OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,FThe escalation follows Israeli Prime
OL,7,FMinister Benjamin Netanyahu's
OL,8,Fannouncement of an expansion in
OL,9,Fmilitary operations in Lebanon,
OL,10,Fapparently triggered by Hezbollah's
OL,11,Fuse of fibre-optic exploding drones
OL,12,Fthat have struck Israeli troops and
OL,13,Freached towns on Israel's northern
OL,14,Fborder.
OL,16,FLebanese and Israeli military
OL,17,Fofficials are set to hold their first
OL,18,Fsecurity talks in Washington on Friday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780002672
OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,FThe talks have extended a fragile
OL,7,Fceasefire that came into effect on
OL,8,FApril 17, though attacks have since
OL,9,Fintensified, while Beirut, Lebanon's
OL,10,Fcapital, has so far been spared.
OL,12,FHezbollah has dismissed the talks and
OL,13,Finstead backed its key ally Iran,
OL,14,Fwhich has made ending the war in
OL,15,FLebanon a condition for its own
OL,16,Fnegotiations with Washington, brokered
OL,17,Fby Pakistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
