FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780002672
OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,FBefore Thursday's attacks, the Israeli
OL,7,Fmilitary's Arabic spokesperson,
OL,8,FAvichay Adraee, issued warnings to
OL,9,Fresidents of eight buildings in the
OL,10,Fcoastal city of Tyre and surrounding
OL,11,Fareas. Many people have since fled.
OL,13,FFurther north, an Israeli drone struck
OL,14,Fan apartment building in the city of
OL,15,FSidon, where some displaced families
OL,16,Fwere living.
OL,18,FMohammad Al-Gharbi, who lived across
OL,19,Fthe road from the building in Sidon,
OL,20,Fwoke up to the sound of the explosion.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
