FL,313,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780002672
OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,F"I was in my room when part of the
OL,7,Fwall and shattered glass fell on me,
OL,8,Fand everything was thrown into chaos,"
OL,9,Fhe said.
OL,11,F"This building that was hit had six
OL,12,Fapartments occupied by poor families
OL,13,Fwho had fled from the south to escape
OL,14,Fthe attacks there, only to be hit
OL,15,Fhere."
OL,17,FIn the nearby coastal town of Adloun,
OL,18,Fan Israeli drone struck a car carrying
OL,19,Fa fleeing family, killing six people,
OL,20,Fincluding children.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@fO]wD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
