OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1780002672
OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,FAnother drone strike, which came
OL,7,Fwithout warning, killed two people on
OL,8,Fa motorcycle near Tyre.
OL,10,FThe target of that attack was not
OL,11,Fimmediately clear, according to
OL,12,FLebanon's National News Agency.
OL,14,FThe Israeli military said a soldier in
OL,15,Fnorthern Israel was killed in a
OL,16,FHezbollah drone attack on Thursday,
OL,17,Fwith two reservists wounded.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
