OL,3,CIsrael intensifies strikes on southern
OL,4,CLebanon ahead of US talks
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHezbollah claimed responsibility for
OL,12,Fdozens of drone and rocket attacks
OL,13,Ftargeting Israeli troops in southern
OL,14,FLebanon and northern Israel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
